Buy one on Amazon: https://lon.tv/e4fup (compensated affiliate link) - Geekom has a nice compact mini PC with a mobile Intel i9 inside. Performance-wise it's not up to par with some of the recent Ryzens we've looked at, but for those wanting Intel this is a decent unit.
